Package controller.part

Class PartMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.part.PartMenu
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddPartController, ModifyPartController
    public abstract class PartMenu
extends java.lang.Object
    PartMenu abstract class provides link to all fxml features on PartMenu.fxml.

    Reducing redundancy between the Add and Modify Part controllers.

    RUNTIME ERROR created the check functions as required to ensure "Max > Inv > Min". When applying them as helpers in the getFieldValues function, took a minute to realize the order mattered. As the checks also gave the variables values, so I kept seeing the "Inv > Max error" since Max was initialized as 0. Could definitely refine the functions more.

    FUTURE ENHANCEMENT set the partSourceListener to return another value other than boolean when another Part Class is added.
